Designed for your daughter (although ‘daughter’ can be edited to a name or whatever you want), the number 14 photo collage is a thoughtful way to give a birthday card with a unique and special quality. The template is set up for you to easily create your own photo collage by adding your photos in order, starting from the top of each number.
